videos.description: Jamari Wheeler picks up the offensive rebound and then while falling out of bounds, he bounces the ball off of Michigan State's Alyza Winston head.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Penn State's Wheeler bounces ball off opponent's head) 2020/2/4

videos.headline: Penn State's Wheeler bounces ball off opponent's head

videos.description: Jamari Wheeler throws a perfect pass up to Mike Watkins who finishes at the rim with a monster slam vs. Michigan State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wheeler and Watkins connect for Penn State oop) 2020/2/4

videos.headline: Wheeler and Watkins connect for Penn State oop

videos.description: Former Michigan State football coach Mark Dantonio addresses the crowd briefly at halftime to thank Spartan fans for their continued support over the years.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Dantonio addresses Michigan State crowd at halftime) 2020/2/4

videos.headline: Dantonio addresses Michigan State crowd at halftime

videos.description: Penn State head coach Pat Chambers is stunned when he receives a technical foul call and has to be restrained by his coaching staff while talking to the refs before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Chambers held back after technical foul call) 2020/2/4

videos.headline: Chambers held back after technical foul call
